<view class='body'>
  <view class='article'>
    <view class="swiper-container">
      <swiper class="swiper_box" autoplay="{{autoplay}}" interval="{{interval}}" duration="{{duration}}" bindchange="swiperchange">
        <block wx:for="{{imgUrls}}" wx:key="id">
          <swiper-item>
            <image bindtap="tapBanner" data-id="{{item}}" data-linkUrl="{{item}}" src="{{item}}" class="slide-image"/>
          </swiper-item>
        </block>
      </swiper>
      <view class="dots">
        <block wx:for="{{imgUrls}}" wx:key="unique">
          <view class="dot{{index == swiperCurrent ? ' active' : ''}}"></view>
        </block>
      </view>
    </view>

    <view class='line-gray'></view>
    <view class='recommend'>服务项目</view>
    <view class='service-items'>
      <view class='up'>
        <navigator url='/pages/modules-list/index?type=copyright'>
          <image src='../../assets/images/zhuanli.png' />
          <text>版权登记中心</text>
          <view class='layer'></view>
        </navigator>
      </view>
      <view class='down'>
        <view class='left'>
          <navigator url='/pages/modules-list/index?type=court'>
            <image src='../../assets/images/court.png' />
            <text>知识产权法院</text>
            <view class='layer'></view>
          </navigator>
        </view>
        <view class='right'>
          <navigator url='/pages/modules-list/index?type=lawyer'>
            <image src='../../assets/images/lawyer.png' />
            <text>知识产权律所</text>
            <view class='layer'></view>
          </navigator>
        </view>
      </view>
    </view>
    <view class='line-gray'></view>
    <view class='recommend'>关于我们</view>
    <view class='about-us'>
      <text>天闻世代知识产权团队是我国最早开展文化版权法律服务的专业团队之一，多年来一直专注于著作权、商标、专利、不正当竞争、娱乐法等服务领域，为央视、新华社、TVB、香港IFPI、阅文集团、味全等知名企业以及政府机构提供常年法律服务。团队承办的多起案件被最高人民法院及京、沪等地方法院评为经典案例，甚至作为全国首例新型案件。迄今，团队为客户索回数亿侵权赔偿款，为多部影视剧提供全程法律顾问服务。无论是团队规模，还是专业程度，天闻世代知识产权团队都处于全国领先地位，能够为不同需求的客户提供全方位的专业法律服务。
</text>
    </view>
    <view class='line-gray'></view>
    <view class='recommend'>联系我们</view>
    <view class='contact-us'>
      <view class='width: 100%;height: 350rpx;overflow:hidden;'>
        <map id="map" longitude="{{longitude}}" latitude="{{latitude}}" markers="{{markers}}" style="width: 100%; height: 350px;">
        </map>
      </view>
      <view class='adress'>
        <text>地址：上海市徐汇区吴中路51号汇豪商务广场1号楼6楼611室</text>
      </view>
      <view class='adress'>
        <text>电话：(86) 021-64734071</text>
      </view>
      <view class='adress call'>
        <button type="default" bindtap="calling">一键拨号</button>
      </view>
    </view>
